{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idc9d4cb7b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598","identifier":"/us/usc/t43/s390rr"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"390rr"},"text":"§ 390rr.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Central Arizona Project","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Lands receiving irrigation water pursuant to a contract with the Secretary as authorized under title III of the Colorado River Basin Project Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/887"},"text":"82 Stat. 887","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1521"},"text":"43 U.S.C. 1521","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) which are placed under recordable contract shall be eligible to receive irrigation water upon terms and conditions related to pricing established by the Secretary pursuant to Federal reclamation law in effect immediately prior to "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-12"},"text":"October 12, 1982","children":[],"tail":", for a period of time not to exceed ten years from the date such lands are capable of being served with irrigation water, as determined by the Secretary."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idc9d4cb7c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/293/tII/s218"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–293, title II, § 218","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/1271"},"text":"96 Stat. 1271","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idc9d4cb7d-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idc9d4cb7e-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idc9d4cb7f-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Colorado River Basin Project Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/537"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–537","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1968-09-30"},"text":"Sept. 30, 1968","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/82/885"},"text":"82 Stat. 885","children":[],"tail":". Title III of the Colorado River Basin Project Act is classified generally to subchapter III (§ 1521 et seq.) of chapter 32 of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s1501"},"text":"section 1501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Federal reclamation law, referred to in text, is defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t43/s390aa"},"text":"section 390aa of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
